ACTION TAKEN:

     On October 24, 2023, Cpl. Heid began an investigation into NCMEC Cybertips 173787319 and 174907342.  The linked tips were sent to NCMEC from Synchronoss Technologies about someone uploading suspected child pornography to their server.  Synchronoss provided the following suspect information:

Phone: 4437226437
Email Address: donnal21911@gmail.com

     Cpl. Heid reviewed the two video files and observed the following:

NCMEC Cybertip 174907342:    Video file 86049c1969fd43ff83884b4a914dab97_09769d3833bf2aa68e26c0066693a3afc27bb96d4441805dfdd9168697d31995 is a two-minute grainy color surveillance stupe video of an adult white male digitally penetrating a young white female before performing oral sex on the child.  The child is reasonably believed to be 10-12 years of age.

NCMEC Cybertip 173787319:   Video file 86049c1969fd43ff83884b4a914dab97_1fd8c0d4895bc8621cb99625df9582d31df19179e0f8d8faaf7abba7c94ce688 is a four minute and thirty-second color video of what appears to be a late teen female having vaginal sex with a presumed adult male.  While the female is having sex, there is a young child that is trying to breastfeed at the same time.

     Using law enforcement databases of the provided phone number 443-722-6437, Cpl. Heid was able to obtain a possible address of 490 New Bridge Road, Rising Sun, MD.  There appears to be a Donna Lee Synder residing at that address which would match the email address of donnal21911.  21911 is the zip code to Rising Sun, MD.  Further investigation revealed that there is a David Joseph Snyder 2nd, 2/M, 6/17/1980 and a David Joseph Snyder 3rd, 2/M, 4/1/2003, also living at the address.  David Snyder is a possible subscriber for the phone.  Cpl. Heid will be conducting further investigation at a later date and anticipating that a search warrant will be conducted on the account.  The case will remain open at this time.

CASE OPEN
